        "execSummary":  "Amazon Quick is a direct enterprise-facing agentic product, not just infrastructure ΓÇö a notable evolution for AWS, which has historically positioned itself as the platform beneath other vendors\u0027 AI products. For customer support and revenue operations leaders, Quick\u0027s end-to-end sales cycle coverage sets a benchmark for what agentic AI teammates look like in practice: cross-system integration, autonomous CRM updates, and contextual meeting prep. The CRM integrations with Salesforce and HubSpot lower the adoption barrier significantly for most enterprise sales orgs. The key question for procurement is whether Quick\u0027s closed-loop automation can be audited and overridden reliably ΓÇö sales AI errors have direct revenue and relationship consequences.",
