        "execSummary":  "The democratization of software creation through AI-native interfaces is not just a developer productivity story ΓÇö it is a structural change in how enterprises build competitive capability. Customer-support leaders who enable domain experts to build and iterate on AI-powered workflows without deep engineering dependencies will move faster than those requiring IT gatekeeping. The 10x framing, while aspirational, is grounded in the measurable reduction of translation costs between business intent and technical execution. The key risk is governance: broader participation in building AI systems without appropriate guardrails can introduce quality and security gaps.",
